{"tid":1226103,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳林鄭月娥暫緩修例 黃秋生寸政府：點解要對「暴動」低頭？","createTime":"2019-06-15T09:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:12:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14f723a8f4d24a99c3d4a696afd56e6bd26448ef","tid":1226103,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"繼6月9日103萬人上街反送中及連日佔領金鐘示威後，建制派對修例意見昨日突然全部「轉軚」，而全部建制派中人均表示應該暫緩執行，根據今日多個報道指，行政長官林鄭月娥今日下午將見傳媒，宣佈暫緩修例。（相關新聞： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2WHgi78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WHgi78&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=715e550f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2WHgi78</a> ）<br />\n近日非常關注反送中條例事件，更常常於社交網站表達見解的黃秋生，今日接受《蘋果》訪問，問到對政府可能宣佈暫緩修例有何睇法時，秋生回覆說：「（政府）點解要對『暴動』低頭？如果唔係『暴動』，係抗議的話，咁點解槍槍打頭呀？咁啲『父親』（警方）使唔使追究呀？」<br />\n秋生又表示林鄭應該落台換人：「佢搞成咁仲叫佢解說？換人啦！都自己射自己龍門咯，同埋，我懷疑佢識唔識得解說。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190615/large/1560573669_0ac0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190615%2Flarge%2F1560573669_0ac0.jpg&h=e3dc35b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190615/59718202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59718202&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=4d5ddb2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59718202&h=b247203f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190615/59718202</a>"},{"pid":"dfd830f9b77028ee99890fbef6ed8d134ecb7e3c","tid":1226103,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224572</a>"},{"pid":"008037010efb21b01011bbeaf4f146d02382a876","tid":1226103,"uid":23160,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:57:46.000Z","msg":"暴動都唔可以打頭囉屌你"},{"pid":"27711ead89c81d4f85434a763d2853cdc9bc924a","tid":1226103,"uid":110570,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;香港政府對暴動低頭&rsquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629487e2c9aca57842243051c8156065bec82187","tid":1226103,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"兩面不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48470509977c5efd8fd85d09b1780d93af48612c","tid":1226103,"uid":73862,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:03:54.000Z","msg":"一個林鄭母親 但有三萬個父親 代表d咩？"},{"pid":"d505db0a0176320dc9a43d6c321cea0c452973f9","tid":1226103,"uid":217162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"秋生哥講啲嘢真係好精警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b501e8d4aae9537047d786ad4d5647856439a89","tid":1226103,"uid":110570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48470509977c5efd8fd85d09b1780d93af48612c","tid":1226103,"uid":73862,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:03:54.000Z","msg":"一個林鄭母親 但有三萬個父親 代表d咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"動物公廁？"},{"pid":"3a390561ae52aa245463c656a5117dc276f59a4e","tid":1226103,"uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzAwGyx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzAwGyx.png&h=01a65b88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"283322f25c16f1d6e36b4e99d5a8e3fe23b30efc","tid":1226103,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score